    <abstract>
      <t>   Existing source address validation (SAV) mechanisms have their own
   core data structures for SAV rules which are coupled with the
   corresponding underlying implementation.  This document defines a
   unified abstraction named SAV table that stores all the SAV rules.
   The abstraction makes it convenient for engineers or operators to
   improve existing SAV mechanisms or properly apply SAV on routers.

	 </t>
